                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Address:</strong> <br>Jl. Brawijaya, Geblagan, Tamantirto, Kec. Kasihan, Kabupaten Bantul, Daerah Istimewa Yogyakarta 55183</li>
                    <li><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> Phone:</strong> <br>0816-830-861 (Gio)</li>
                </ul>
